OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777036267
OL,3,CTwo men convicted over plot to land
OL,4,Cinflatable packed with cocaine into
OL,5,CWatchet
OL,7,FTwo men who were part of a plot to
OL,8,Fbring cocaine with a street value of
OL,9,F#26.5 million into the UK through the
OL,10,FNorth Somerset coast have been
OL,11,Fconvicted, with one of them jailed for
OL,12,Fmore than 20 years.
OL,14,FColin Benson and Joshua Rose waited at
OL,15,FWatchet for an inflatable to bring the
OL,16,Fhaul ashore and fled after officers
OL,17,Ffrom the National Crime Agency swooped
OL,18,Fin.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
