OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777036267
OL,3,CTwo men convicted over plot to land
OL,4,Cinflatable packed with cocaine into
OL,5,CWatchet
OL,7,FBenson, 60, and 38-year-old Rose drove
OL,8,Fin a convoy back home to Preston, in
OL,9,FLancashire, during the early hours of
OL,10,FJuly 31 last year - while four other
OL,11,Fmen were arrested by officers at the
OL,12,Fscene, and the inflatable was seized.
OL,14,FIt was searched and found to contain
OL,15,F14 large bale-sized packages,
OL,16,Fcontaining a further 322 smaller
OL,17,Fpackages weighing a kilo each.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777036267
OL,3,CTwo men convicted over plot to land
OL,4,Cinflatable packed with cocaine into
OL,5,CWatchet
OL,7,FNCA officers arrested Rose and Benson
OL,8,Fin Lancashire in November 2025. A jury
OL,9,Fat North Somerset Crown Court
OL,10,Fconvicted Benson of being knowingly
OL,11,Fconcerned in the importation of
OL,12,Fcocaine on April 22 following a two-
OL,13,Fweek trial. Rose pleaded guilty to an
OL,14,Foffence of participating in the
OL,15,Factivities of an organised crime group
OL,16,Fat an earlier hearing.
OL,18,FBenson was today (Thursday, April 23)
OL,19,Fsentenced to 20 years and six months
OL,20,Fimprisonment. Rose will be sentenced
OL,21,Fat a later date.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777036267
OL,3,CTwo men convicted over plot to land
OL,4,Cinflatable packed with cocaine into
OL,5,CWatchet
OL,7,FThe other men involved pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto drugs importation charges last year
OL,9,Fand have been sentenced to a total of
OL,10,F49 years.
OL,12,FFootage from the NCA showed the group
OL,13,Fin their boat at Watchet Harbour
OL,15,FNCA Senior Investigating Officer Alan
OL,16,FFrench said: "Benson and Rose adopted
OL,17,Fthe role of bystanders and clearly
OL,18,Fdidn't want to embark on such a risky
OL,19,Fjourney to collect this valuable cargo.
OL,26,@xD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
