OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777036267
OL,3,CTwo men convicted over plot to land
OL,4,Cinflatable packed with cocaine into
OL,5,CWatchet
OL,7,F"However, they played a central role
OL,8,Fin planning the conspiracy through the
OL,9,Fnumerous trips made down south.
OL,11,F"When their accomplices were arrested,
OL,12,Fthey knew the game was up and left the
OL,13,Fscene in haste.
OL,15,F"It's possible they thought that law
OL,16,Fenforcement wouldn't bother to arrest
OL,17,Fthem and make them accountable for
OL,18,Ftheir crimes, but the NCA will never
OL,19,Fcease in bringing those involved in
OL,20,Fsmuggling class A drugs to justice.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
