OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777036267
OL,3,CTwo men convicted over plot to land
OL,4,Cinflatable packed with cocaine into
OL,5,CWatchet
OL,7,F"The NCA tackles at-sea drugs drop-
OL,8,Foffs as a priority to ensure illegal
OL,9,Fdrugs do not make it to UK shores.
OL,10,FDedicated Officers from the NCA were
OL,11,Faided by, and are grateful for, the
OL,12,Fvital support of, our partners in
OL,13,FBorder Force, the South West Regional
OL,14,FOrganised Crime Unit, Avon and
OL,15,FSomerset Police and Devon and Cornwall
OL,16,FPolice."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@HO]
